onal left-side footrest allow for a more natural stretch-out experience and enhanced comfort.</p></div><div class="Tabs_descriptionItem__QECXo"><p class="Tabs_description__g2DaU">NIO ES8 redefines third-row comfort with power-adjustable cushions that slide back and forth with a 130 mm range, and backrests that recline up to 130°. </p></div><div class="Tabs_descriptionItem__QECXo"><p class="Tabs_description__g2DaU">The seat system adopts a 15-layer structure, using flagship-level materials from the surfaces to the underlying frame, balancing softness and dynamic support for lasting comfort.</p></div></div></div></div></section><div class="HeroZoomIn_pinSpacer__CV_vM"><section id="hero-zoom-in-interior" class="HeroZoomIn_container__RfDQS HeroZoomIn_dark__qFKZc" style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)"><div class="HeroZoomIn_wrapper__vBA8k"><div class="HeroZoomIn_frame__7z6W9"><div class="HeroZoomIn_mediaContainer__0bFPb"><div class="ImageAndVideo_imageAndVideo__qG5SK HeroZoomIn_media__2MplH HeroZoomIn_active__dqv11"><picture class="responsive-image--picture"><source srcSet="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/interior/interior-details-hero-mobile.jpg" media="(max-width: 1023px)"/><img src="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/interior/interior-details-hero-desktop.jpg" title="" alt="" loading="lazy" class="ResponsiveImage_responsiveImage__OVw0A" draggable="false"/></picture></div></div><div class="HeroZoomIn_overlayContainer__zKHNn"><div class="HeroZoomIn_overlayMask__dHMUd"></div><div class="HeroZoomIn_overlayWrapper__24YMJ"><div class="HeroZoomIn_overlayHeader__uCqfq"><p class="HeroZoomIn_overlayTitle__moggz">Smart Cabin </p></div><div class="HeroZoomIn_overlayFooter__B6DcW"></div></div></div></div></div></section></div><section id="carousel-gallery-interior-details" class="CarouselGallery_container__sxYJ7 CarouselGallery_dark__yZmHw" style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)"><div class="CarouselGallery_galleryScrollContainer_