rs a temperature range from -2°C to 55°C, and a spacious 8.8L capacity. It also provides six smart modes with low power consumption and long standby.</p></div></div></div><div class="grid-col-md-5-abs grid-col-lg-5-abs grid-col-xl-5-abs CarouselGallery_item___mPXK"><div class="ImageAndVideo_imageAndVideo__qG5SK CarouselGallery_media__qPl__"><picture class="responsive-image--picture"><source srcSet="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/interior/interior-details-carousel-03-mobile.jpg" media="(max-width: 1023px)"/><img src="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/interior/interior-details-carousel-03-desktop.jpg" title="Smart Five-Zone Climate Control" alt="Smart Five-Zone Climate Control" loading="lazy" class="ResponsiveImage_responsiveImage__OVw0A" draggable="false"/></picture></div><div class="CarouselGallery_content__Eg4Wu"><div class="CarouselGallery_contentWrapper__Jh_6h"><p class="CarouselGallery_title__Ojlt6">Smart Five-Zone Climate Control</p><p class="CarouselGallery_desc__2hni6">The five-zone climate system allows independent control, ensuring personalized comfort for every seat. When parked under the sun, Overheat Protection Mode keeps the cabin temperature below 40 °C.</p></div></div></div><div class="grid-col-md-5-abs grid-col-lg-5-abs grid-col-xl-5-abs CarouselGallery_item___mPXK"><div class="ImageAndVideo_imageAndVideo__qG5SK CarouselGallery_media__qPl__"><picture class="responsive-image--picture"><source srcSet="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/interior/interior-details-carousel-04-mobile.jpg" media="(max-width: 1023px)"/><img src="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/interior/interior-details-carousel-04-desktop.jpg" title="全方位五星健康座舱_蔚来全新ES8" alt="全方位五星健康座舱_蔚来全新ES8-NIO蔚来官网" loading="lazy" class="ResponsiveImage_responsiveImage__OVw0A" draggable="false"/></picture></div><div class="CarouselGallery_content__Eg4Wu"><div class="CarouselGallery_contentWrapper__Jh_6h"><p class="Ca