*Optional feature</p></div></div></div></div></div></section></div><section id="carousel-gallery-safety" class="CarouselGallery_container__sxYJ7 CarouselGallery_dark__yZmHw" style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)"><div class="CarouselGallery_galleryScrollContainer__kijC3"><div class="CarouselGallery_galleryContainer___oTYO"><div class="CarouselGallery_galleryWrapper__hJ_T_"><div class="grid-col-md-5-abs grid-col-lg-5-abs grid-col-xl-5-abs CarouselGallery_item___mPXK"><div class="ImageAndVideo_imageAndVideo__qG5SK CarouselGallery_media__qPl__"><picture class="responsive-image--picture"><source srcSet="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/safety/safety-details-carousel-01-mobile.jpg" media="(max-width: 1023px)"/><img src="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/safety/safety-details-carousel-01-desktop.jpg" title="Brighter, Broader Low Beams" alt="Brighter, Broader Low Beams" loading="lazy" class="ResponsiveImage_responsiveImage__OVw0A" draggable="false"/></picture></div><div class="CarouselGallery_content__Eg4Wu"><div class="CarouselGallery_contentWrapper__Jh_6h"><p class="CarouselGallery_title__Ojlt6">Brighter, Broader Low Beams</p><p class="CarouselGallery_desc__2hni6">The micro-LED low-beam enhancement technology effectively concentrates lights within 30 to 50m, illuminating six lanes 50 meters away, with the brightness improved by 80%.</p></div></div></div><div class="grid-col-md-5-abs grid-col-lg-5-abs grid-col-xl-5-abs CarouselGallery_item___mPXK"><div class="ImageAndVideo_imageAndVideo__qG5SK CarouselGallery_media__qPl__"><picture class="responsive-image--picture"><source srcSet="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/safety/safety-details-carousel-02-mobile.jpg" media="(max-width: 1023px)"/><img src="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/safety/safety-details-carousel-02-desktop.jpg" title="Farther, Sharper High Beams" alt="Farther, Sharper High Beams" loading="lazy" class="ResponsiveImag