hide-on-desktop'/>Imaging Radar</span></li><li class="Tabs_tabItem__fJ0JF"><span class="Tabs_tabItemLabel__RHqGX">8 MP High-Resolution <br class='hide-on-desktop'/>Cameras</span></li></ul></div><div class="Tabs_descriptionContainer__t5wUG undefined"><div class="Tabs_descriptionItem__QECXo Tabs_isActive__pG3nc"><p class="Tabs_description__g2DaU Tabs_isActive__pG3nc">Featuring the original watchtower layout and the inhouse developed NX6031 chip, it delivers a maximum detection range of 500m, offering clear, far, and wide vision for safety. </p></div><div class="Tabs_descriptionItem__QECXo"><p class="Tabs_description__g2DaU">Ultra-high-resolution LiDARs with a maximum field of view of 120° horizontally and 70° vertically, reaching up to 150m for side detection.</p></div><div class="Tabs_descriptionItem__QECXo"><p class="Tabs_description__g2DaU">Able to detect objects as far as 370m, it has exceptional penetration capability that significantly enhances sensing in complex conditions and adverse weathers, taking driving safety to the next level.</p></div><div class="Tabs_descriptionItem__QECXo"><p class="Tabs_description__g2DaU">Seven 8 MP cameras provide 360° high-resolution surround vision. Combined with the top-tier ISP capability of NX9031, they deliver a great boost to perception. </p></div></div></div></div></section><div id="horizontal-rule-intelligent-driving" class="HorizontalRule_container__wwmZ0 HorizontalRule_dark__DbS2Q" style="background-color:rgba(21, 21, 21, 1)"><div class="grid-container"><div class="grid-col-sm-2 grid-col-md-10 grid-col-lg-10 grid-col-xl-10 grid-offset-md-1 grid-offset-lg-1 grid-offset-xl-1"><div class="copy-container"><hr class="HorizontalRule_hr__k_IpX"/></div></div></div></div><section id="carousel-tabs-intelligent-driving-nwm" class="CarouselTabsSolo_container__vjkoH CarouselTabsSolo_dark__hUy7u" style="background-color:rgba(21, 21, 21, 1)"><header class="CarouselHeader_container__Z8rXi CarouselHeader_dark__i_6oI"><div class="grid-co