raggable="false"/></picture></div><div class="CarouselTabsSolo_paginationArrow__d8FWy CarouselTabsSolo_paginationArrowNext__FsHmr"><picture class="responsive-image--picture"><img src="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/common/arrows/arrow-filled-black-next.svg" title="" alt="" loading="lazy" class="ResponsiveImage_responsiveImage__OVw0A" draggable="false"/></picture></div></div><div class="Tabs_tabsContainer__mDe3I" data-theme="dark" data-accent-color="false"><ul class="Tabs_tabs__JdVWb" data-scrollable="false"><li class="Tabs_tabItem__fJ0JF Tabs_tabItemActive__DRBJv"><span class="Tabs_tabItemLabel__RHqGX">Point-to-Point NOP+ </span></li><li class="Tabs_tabItem__fJ0JF"><span class="Tabs_tabItemLabel__RHqGX">Intelligent Parking Assist</span></li><li class="Tabs_tabItem__fJ0JF"><span class="Tabs_tabItemLabel__RHqGX">NIO WorldModel</span></li></ul></div><div class="Tabs_descriptionContainer__t5wUG undefined"><div class="Tabs_descriptionItem__QECXo Tabs_isActive__pG3nc"><p class="Tabs_description__g2DaU Tabs_isActive__pG3nc">Covering all scenarios from urban areas, office complexes, and car parks to highways, urban expressways, and recharging locations, NIO Navigate on Pilot Plus (NOP+) delivers a smarter, easier, and safer pilot experience from point to point.</p></div><div class="Tabs_descriptionItem__QECXo"><p class="Tabs_description__g2DaU">Even a large three-row SUV can park with ease and grace. With features including Shiftless Advanced Parking Assist, Remote Parking, Drag-and-Park, and Power Swap Pilot, the system adapts flexibly to every scenario like a skillful human driver, able to park in any spot you see. </p></div><div class="Tabs_descriptionItem__QECXo"><p class="Tabs_description__g2DaU">As the world’s first multivariable autoregressive generative model for smart driving, it generates 216 parallel trajectory possibilities every 0.1 second, evaluates them, and selects the optimal path. With cutting-edge architecture and algorithms, it delivers an efficient intelligent and assisted driving experience.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id="carousel-cards-nad" class="CarouselCards_container__XvCOK" style="background-color:rgba(21, 21, 21, 1);padding-top:0"><div class="AnimationWrapper_wrapper__SftXd AnimationWrapper_opacity_0__W4ib0 AnimationWrapper_transformy_20__SU0pm"><div class="grid-container CarouselCards_cardList__GFUdx"><div data-effect="normal" class="grid-col-sm-2-abs grid-col-md-4-abs grid-col-lg-4-abs grid-col-xl-4-abs CardNormal_card__mfA_5 CardNormal_dark__mEpzw"><div class="CardNormal_media__C_oM3"><div class="ImageAndVideo_imageAndVideo__qG5SK"><picture class="responsive-image--picture"><source srcSet="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/AD/nad-carousel-01-mobile.jpg" media="(max-width: 1023px)"/><img src="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/AD/nad-carousel-01-desktop.jpg" title="" alt="" loading="lazy" class="ResponsiveImage_responsiveImage__OVw0A" draggable="false"/></picture></div></div><div class="CardNormal_cardContent__tqpNB"><div class="CardNormal_cardContentWrapper__kzZeI"><h3 class="CardNormal_title__Fqz0p">NX9031, Designed for Smart Driving </h3><p class="CardNormal_description__wPKWU">The inhouse-developed automotive-grade chip, NX9031, built for NIO WorldModel, delivers exceptional performance on par with four flagship chips.</p></div></div></div><div data-effect="normal" class="grid-col-sm-2-abs grid-col-md-4-abs grid-col-lg-4-abs grid-col-xl-4-abs CardNormal_card__mfA_5 CardNormal_dark__mEpzw"><div class="CardNormal_media__C_oM3"><div class="ImageAndVideo_imageAndVideo__qG5SK"><picture class="responsive-image--picture"><source srcSet="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/AD/nad-carousel-02-mobile.jpg" media="(max-width: 1023px)"/><img src="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/AD/nad-carousel-02-desktop.jpg" title="" alt="" loading="lazy" class="ResponsiveImage_responsiveImage__OVw0A" draggable="false"/></picture></div></div><div class="CardNormal_cardContent__tqpNB"><div class="CardNormal_cardContentWrapper__kzZeI"><h3 class="CardNormal_title__Fqz0p">Cedar ADAM Central Computing Cluster</h3><p class="CardNormal_description__wPKWU">The high-performance, upgradable, and scalable brain for smart EVs, featuring an NX9031, NIO’s inhouse developed automotive-grade smart driving chip, and a Qualcomm SA8295P.</p></div></div></div><div data-effect="normal" class="grid-col-sm-2-abs grid-col-md-4-abs grid-col-lg-4-abs grid-col-xl-4-abs CardNormal_card__mfA_5 CardNormal_dark__mEpzw"><div class="CardNormal_media__C_oM3"><div class="ImageAndVideo_imageAndVideo__qG5SK"><picture class="responsive-image--picture"><source srcSet="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/AD/nad-carousel-03-mobile.jpg" media="(max-width: 1023px)"/><img src="https://cdn-udp-public.eu.nio.com/www-nio/es8-2025/nd25/AD/nad-carousel-03-desktop.jpg" title="" alt="" loading="lazy" class="ResponsiveImage_responsiveImage__OVw0A" draggable="false"/></picture></div></div><div class="CardNormal_cardContent__tqpNB"><div class="CardNormal_cardContentWrapper__kzZeI"><h3 class="CardNormal_title__Fqz0p">NIO Vehicle Operating System</h3><p class="CardNormal_description__wPKWU">An AI-oriented vehicle OS that seamlessly integrates smart driving, smart cabin, and chassis operations, delivering an efficient, safe, intelligent, and enjoyable digital experience.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="AnimationWrapper_wrapper__SftXd AnimationWrapper_opacity_0__W4ib0 AnimationWrapper_transformy_20__SU0pm"><div class="grid-container"><div class="grid-col-sm-2 grid-col-md-12 grid-col-lg-12 grid-col-xl-12 CarouselCards_disclaimerContainer__M1aad"><div class="copy-container"><p class="CarouselCards_disclaimer__nNHTN">*The features shown in the Assisted and Intelligent Driving section rolls out progressively starting from the second quarter of 2025.</p><p class="CarouselCards_disclaimer__nNHTN">*All con